  '["Punctul de control G1","Punctul de control G2","Punctul de control M (al fusului)","Punctul de control S","Nu există un astfel de punct de control"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'The G2 checkpoint verifies that DNA replication in S phase was completed successfully before the cell enters mitosis.',
