  'hard',
  'CRISPR-Cas9 technology allows scientists to:',
  'Tehnologia CRISPR-Cas9 permite oamenilor de știință să:',
  '["Only study proteins","Precisely edit DNA sequences in cells","Only observe cell division","Prevent all cell death","Only study RNA"]'::jsonb,
