  '["Țesut nervos","Mușchi cardiac","Țesut epitelial","Mușchi scheletic","Cartilaj"]'::jsonb,
  2,
  'Epithelial tissue has high regenerative capacity due to rapid cell division, especially in areas like skin and intestinal lining.',
