  '["Țesut conjunctiv matur","Țesut conjunctiv embrionar care dă naștere tuturor țesuturilor conjunctive","Un tip de mușchi","Precursor al țesutului nervos","Epiteliu matur"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Mesenchyme is embryonic connective tissue derived from mesoderm; it differentiates into all types of adult connective tissue.',
