  '["Epidermis","Dermis","Hypodermis","Stratum corneum","Subcutaneous fat only"]'::jsonb,
  '["Epidermă","Dermă","Hipodermă","Stratul corneu","Doar grăsimea subcutanată"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'The dermis is the thick layer beneath the epidermis; it is connective tissue containing vessels, nerves, appendages, and glands.',
