  '["Keratinocytes","Melanocytes","Langerhans cells (dendritic cells)","Merkel cells","Fibroblasts"]'::jsonb,
  '["Keratinocite","Melanocite","Celule Langerhans (celule dendritice)","Celule Merkel","Fibroblaste"]'::jsonb,
  2,
  'Langerhans cells are dendritic cells that act as antigen-presenting cells, initiating immune responses in the skin.',
