  'Port-wine stains (nevus flammeus) are vascular birthmarks caused by dilated dermal capillaries, appearing as flat, red-purple patches.',
  'Petele de vin de Porto (nevus flammeus) sunt semne de naștere vasculare cauzate de capilare dermice dilatate, apărând ca pete plate, roșii-purpurii.',
