  'Lichen planus presents with the "5 Ps": Purple, Polygonal, Planar (flat-topped), Pruritic Papules, often with Wickham striae.',
  'Lichenul plan prezintă „cele 5 P-uri": Purpuriu, Poligonal, Plan (cu vârf plat), Papule Pruriginoase, adesea cu strii Wickham.',
