  '["Build new bone","Break down (resorb) bone tissue","Store calcium","Produce cartilage","Maintain bone homeostasis only"]'::jsonb,
  '["Construi os nou","Distruge (resorbi) țesut osos","Stoca calciu","Produce cartilaj","Menține doar homeostazia osoasă"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Osteoclasts are large, multinucleated cells that resorb bone by secreting acids and enzymes, important for bone remodeling.',
