  '["Thin filaments","Thick filaments","Z discs","Sarcolemma","Mitochondria"]'::jsonb,
  '["Filamentelor subțiri","Filamentelor groase","Discurilor Z","Sarcolemei","Mitocondriilor"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Myosin forms the thick filaments and has heads that bind to actin during the cross-bridge cycle.',
