  '["Cytoplasm of muscle fiber","Plasma membrane of muscle fiber","Contractile protein","Connective tissue covering","Nucleus of muscle cell"]'::jsonb,
  '["Citoplasma fibrei musculare","Membrana plasmatică a fibrei musculare","Proteină contractilă","Înveliș de țesut conjunctiv","Nucleul celulei musculare"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'The sarcolemma is the specialized plasma membrane of a muscle fiber that conducts action potentials.',
