  '["Skeletal muscle","Cardiac muscle","Smooth muscle","All muscle types","Nervous tissue"]'::jsonb,
  '["Mușchi scheletic","Mușchi cardiac","Mușchi neted","Toate tipurile de mușchi","Țesut nervos"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Intercalated discs are unique to cardiac muscle, containing gap junctions and desmosomes for electrical and mechanical coupling.',
