  'med-admission-barrons',
  'medium',
  'The dihydropyridine receptor (DHPR) is located on:',
  'Receptorul dihidropiridinic (DHPR) este localizat pe:',
  '["Sarcoplasmic reticulum","T-tubule membrane","Sarcolemma surface only","Nucleus","Mitochondria"]'::jsonb,
  '["Reticul sarcoplasmic","Membrana tubulilor T","Doar suprafața sarcolemei","Nucleu","Mitocondrii"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'DHPRs are voltage-sensitive receptors on T-tubules that detect depolarization and trigger Ca²⁺ release from the SR.',
