  'easy',
  'Which structure connects the middle ear to the pharynx?',
  'Care structură conectează urechea mijlocie la faringe?',
  '["External auditory canal","Eustachian tube","Semicircular canal","Cochlear duct","Oval window"]'::jsonb,
  '["Conductul auditiv extern","Tuba lui Eustachio","Canalul semicircular","Ductul cohlear","Fereastra ovală"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'The Eustachian (auditory) tube connects the middle ear to the nasopharynx, allowing pressure equalization.',
