  'med-admission-barrons',
  'medium',
  'What causes glaucoma?',
  'Ce cauzează glaucomul?',
  '["Clouding of the lens","Increased intraocular pressure damaging the optic nerve","Infection of the cornea","Detachment of the retina","Absence of cone cells"]'::jsonb,
  '["Opacifierea cristalinului","Creșterea presiunii intraoculare care lezează nervul optic","Infecție a corneei","Dezlipirea retinei","Absența celulelor con"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Glaucoma is characterized by increased intraocular pressure that can damage the optic nerve, leading to vision loss.',
