  '["Pacinian corpuscle","Meissner''s corpuscle","Ruffini ending","Free nerve ending","Golgi tendon organ"]'::jsonb,
  '["Corpusculul Pacinian","Corpusculul Meissner","Terminația Ruffini","Terminație nervoasă liberă","Organul tendinos Golgi"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Meissner''s corpuscles are rapidly adapting mechanoreceptors in the dermal papillae, sensitive to light touch and texture.',
