  'easy',
  'Which hormone increases blood glucose by stimulating glycogen breakdown?',
  'Care hormon crește glicemia stimulând degradarea glicogenului?',
  '["Insulin","Glucagon","Calcitonin","Aldosterone","Melatonin"]'::jsonb,
  '["Insulina","Glucagonul","Calcitonina","Aldosteronul","Melatonina"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Glucagon, from pancreatic alpha cells, stimulates glycogenolysis (glycogen breakdown) in the liver to raise blood glucose.',
