  '["Thyroid cancer","Graves'' disease","Hashimoto''s thyroiditis","Iodine deficiency","Pituitary tumor"]'::jsonb,
  '["Cancer tiroidian","Boala Graves","Tiroidita Hashimoto","Deficit de iod","Tumoare hipofizară"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Graves'' disease, an autoimmune disorder with TSH receptor-stimulating antibodies, is the most common cause of hyperthyroidism.',
  'Boala Graves, o tulburare autoimună cu anticorpi care stimulează receptorii TSH, este cea mai frecventă cauză de hipertiroidism.',
