  '["Deficit de iod","Tiroidita Hashimoto","Boala Graves","Cancer tiroidian","Tumoare hipofizară"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Hashimoto''s thyroiditis is an autoimmune destruction of the thyroid and the most common cause of hypothyroidism where iodine is sufficient.',
