  'hard',
  'The Frank-Starling law states that:',
  'Legea Frank-Starling afirmă că:',
  '["Heart rate increases with exercise","Stroke volume increases with increased venous return","Blood pressure equals cardiac output times resistance","Vessels dilate when blood flow increases","Heart rate is controlled by the SA node"]'::jsonb,
