  '["Skeletal muscle pump","Respiratory pump","Venous valves","Venodilation","Increased blood volume"]'::jsonb,
  '["Pompa musculară scheletică","Pompa respiratorie","Valvele venoase","Venodilatația","Volumul de sânge crescut"]'::jsonb,
  3,
  'Venodilation increases venous capacitance, reducing venous return (blood pools in veins).',
