  'medium',
  'Terminal bronchioles lead to:',
  'Bronhiolele terminale duc la:',
  '["Trachea","Primary bronchi","Respiratory bronchioles","Alveolar ducts directly","Pleural cavity"]'::jsonb,
  '["Trahee","Bronhii primare","Bronhiole respiratorii","Ducte alveolare direct","Cavitatea pleurală"]'::jsonb,
  2,
  'Terminal bronchioles branch into respiratory bronchioles, which have some alveoli in their walls.',
