  '["Renină","25-hidroxilază","1-alfa hidroxilază","Anhidrază carbonică","ECA"]'::jsonb,
  2,
  '1-alpha hydroxylase in proximal tubule cells converts 25-hydroxyvitamin D to active 1,25-dihydroxyvitamin D (calcitriol).',
