  '["Epididim","Ductul ejaculator","Ureter","Doar uretra prostatică","Ductul bulbouretral"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'The ejaculatory duct is formed where the vas deferens and the seminal vesicle duct join; it passes through the prostate and empties into the urethra.',
