  'hard',
  'What is the sequence of cells in spermatogenesis?',
  'Care este secvența celulelor în spermatogeneză?',
  '["Spermatid → Spermatocyte → Spermatogonium → Sperm","Spermatogonium → Primary spermatocyte → Secondary spermatocyte → Spermatid → Sperm","Sperm → Spermatid → Spermatocyte → Spermatogonium","Primary spermatocyte → Spermatogonium → Spermatid → Sperm","Secondary spermatocyte → Primary spermatocyte → Spermatid → Sperm"]'::jsonb,
  '["Spermatidă → Spermatocit → Spermatogonie → Spermatozoid","Spermatogonie → Spermatocit primar → Spermatocit secundar → Spermatidă → Spermatozoid","Spermatozoid → Spermatidă → Spermatocit → Spermatogonie","Spermatocit primar → Spermatogonie → Spermatidă → Spermatozoid","Spermatocit secundar → Spermatocit primar → Spermatidă → Spermatozoid"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Spermatogenesis proceeds from spermatogonium (2n) → primary spermatocyte (2n) → secondary spermatocyte (n) → spermatid (n) → spermatozoon (n).',
  'Spermatogeneza progresează de la spermatogonie (2n) → spermatocit primar (2n) → spermatocit secundar (n) → spermatidă (n) → spermatozoid (n).',
  'repro-male',
  5
) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
