  '["Celule granuloase","Celule tecale","Corona radiată","Zona pelucidă","Cumulus oophorus"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Theca cells form the outer layer of the follicle and produce androgens that are converted to estrogen by granulosa cells.',
