  '["Release of the egg from ovary","Shedding of the uterine lining","Fertilization of the egg","Implantation of embryo","Formation of the corpus luteum"]'::jsonb,
  '["Eliberarea ovulului din ovar","Eliminarea mucoasei uterine","Fertilizarea ovulului","Implantarea embrionului","Formarea corpului galben"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Menstruation is the shedding of the endometrial lining when pregnancy does not occur, triggered by declining progesterone levels.',
