  'medium',
  'What is oogenesis?',
  'Ce este ovogeneza?',
  '["Formation of sperm","Formation of female gametes (eggs)","Fertilization","Implantation","Menstruation"]'::jsonb,
  '["Formarea spermatozoizilor","Formarea gameților feminini (ovule)","Fertilizare","Implantare","Menstruație"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Oogenesis is the process of egg cell (oocyte) formation that begins before birth and is completed at fertilization.',
