  'medium',
  'What causes the change in cervical mucus at ovulation?',
  'Ce cauzează schimbarea mucusului cervical la ovulație?',
  '["Progesterone increase","Estrogen peak causing thin, stretchy mucus (spinnbarkeit)","LH decrease","FSH increase","Prolactin release"]'::jsonb,
  '["Creșterea progesteronului","Vârful de estrogen cauzând mucus subțire, elastic (spinnbarkeit)","Scăderea LH","Creșterea FSH","Eliberarea prolactinei"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'High estrogen at ovulation makes cervical mucus thin, watery, and stretchy (spinnbarkeit), facilitating sperm transport.',
