  'medium',
  'What type of epithelium lines the fallopian tubes?',
  'Ce tip de epiteliu tapetează trompele uterine?',
  '["Stratified squamous","Simple ciliated columnar epithelium","Transitional","Simple squamous","Pseudostratified non-ciliated"]'::jsonb,
  '["Pavimentos stratificat","Epiteliu cilindric ciliat simplu","Tranzițional","Pavimentos simplu","Pseudostratificat neciliat"]'::jsonb,
