  'medium',
  'What is the round ligament of the uterus?',
  'Ce este ligamentul rotund al uterului?',
  '["Supports the ovary","Fibromuscular cord from uterus through inguinal canal to labia majora","Attaches uterus to sacrum","Part of the broad ligament only","Supports the bladder"]'::jsonb,
