  '["Serous cystadenocarcinoma","Mature teratoma (dermoid cyst)","Mucinous cystadenoma","Granulosa cell tumor","Dysgerminoma"]'::jsonb,
  '["Cistadenocarcinom seros","Teratom matur (chist dermoid)","Cistadenom mucinos","Tumoră cu celule granuloase","Disgerminom"]'::jsonb,
  1,
  'Mature teratomas (dermoid cysts) are the most common ovarian tumors in young women, containing tissue from all three germ layers.',
  'Teratoamele mature (chisturi dermoide) sunt cele mai frecvente tumori ovariene la femeile tinere, conținând țesut din toate cele trei straturi germinale.',
