  'What is trisomy 18 (Edwards syndrome)?',
  'Ce este trisomia 18 (sindromul Edwards)?',
  '["Extra sex chromosome","Three copies of chromosome 18 with severe abnormalities, usually lethal","Missing chromosome","Translocation","Mosaicism only"]'::jsonb,
  '["Cromozom sexual suplimentar","Trei copii ale cromozomului 18 cu anomalii severe, de obicei letale","Cromozom lipsă","Translocație","Doar mozaicism"]'::jsonb,
