  'emb62',
  'med-admission-barrons',
  'hard',
  'What is Turner syndrome?',
  'Ce este sindromul Turner?',
  '["XXY karyotype","45,XO karyotype - female with missing X chromosome","XYY karyotype","XXX karyotype","Normal female"]'::jsonb,
  '["Cariotip XXY","Cariotip 45,XO - femeie cu cromozom X lipsă","Cariotip XYY","Cariotip XXX","Femeie normală"]'::jsonb,
